{
  "stem": "1479.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yes, we used to see Schindler.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we used to see him less.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The only thing, they were still till the last moment-- and we must remember, this is already '45.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Of course, the Nazis knew how the war was coming to the end.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the Nazi women, till the last moment, what they did, how they were treating us-- because they were certain, you know, that the day would come.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "As you already know about it, the mass grave was prepared for us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Nobody didn't enter to the Nazi's mind that maybe something can happen unexpected, and some people will survive them over there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were positive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were sure nobody will come out from there alive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is not even nice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like for instance, we were working.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after all, they had nothing to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they found things to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When they would-- when they decided, they would come and they would say, this row of machines, whoever's operating now, you are going to the latrine.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Not when you need it, but when they felt.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And also, the way they did it-- so dehumanized, so to degrade us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It is unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they would-- we would follow her because the latrine was in the courtyard outside the main building.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So she would say, now-- is only [GERMAN] kommander.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, this sounds horrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that's how they looked at us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They treated us less than human.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then, they would take us, another group, another time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was [GERMAN] kommander.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This is awful!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's what they were doing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when we were waiting in, in line, because we were entering one at a time-- and this was in the spring.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we saw the sun.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we turned our eyes to the skies.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
